{"_path":"/fitness/f001","_dir":"fitness","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"TRX 運動","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":1,"category":"室內運動","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-26T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"trx-運動"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRX 運動"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"trx-簡介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRX 簡介："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRX 為「Total body Resistance eXercise」的縮寫，最早源自於美軍海豹突襲隊隊員(U.S. Navy SEALs)、亦為 Fitness Anywhere 創辦人 - Rndy Hetrick 所設計之戰地訓練概念，在缺乏資源的戰場環境中，利用修船工具將降落傘帶與握把縫製成最初的原型訓練繩，經過改良與研發後成為現在受歡迎的 TRX。它不受場地限制，擁有強化核心肌群的超強效果，更是一種方便、有效、可以隨身攜帶，而且適合各種體能的懸吊訓練工具。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRX 懸吊訓練是利用身體重量做為阻力，可自行調整傾斜角度或站姿來控制合適的強度，適用於各種體能程度的使用者。獨特的懸吊原理能增加全身肌群的平衡、協調與穩定，讓您運動到連自己都不曉得的身體部位，對於強化肌力、核心肌群、燃燒脂肪、雕塑曲線有極佳的效果。TRX 懸吊訓練繩體積巧可隨身攜帶，無論是在家中或是出差旅行，只需要一個懸吊點（如單槓、柱子或門檔 Door Anchor 等）就能隨時隨地進行健身及訓練，超過 300 種以上的訓練動作，可依人體的活動有無限的變化性，配合多樣化的運動課程，讓 TRX 成為最迷你、最多功能的全方位的訓練器材。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"訓練規劃"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"訓練規劃"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"認識 TRX，練習在懸吊訓練系統上，控制與地心引力間的平衡: 肢體勿碰觸摩擦繩子、勿鋸狀移動拉扯平衡圈"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"熱身、伸展及基本核心訓練: 訓練過程中保持繩子張力、動作過程體線維持平衡"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大肌群與核心肌群穩定性加強"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"強度應用訓練: 秒數計時訓練、底面積原則、向量原則及鐘擺原則之應用操作"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"功能性訓練及運動能力加強: 運動復健、柔軟度加強訓練"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"trx-繩的注意事項"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRX 繩的注意事項"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用 TRX 繩時要在能力範圍內把握對阻力大小的調節，不要急於挑戰高難度的動作。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由於 TRX 繩軌跡不固定，所以不適合抗阻的初學者，容易導致受傷。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"對於大重量增肌的人，不太適合，TRX 繩不方便加大重量。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"動作不規範或者錯誤的姿勢容易使肌肉和韌帶受傷, 最好找專業教練指導後實施"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"trx-裝備採購"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TRX 裝備採購"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://24h.pchome.com.tw/prod/DEBY9I-A9009BZX3?fq=/S/DEBYAO"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PCHome:\n        康生 Concern CON-FE604"}]},{"type":"text","value":"全身核心肌群TRX懸掛式吊繩訓練帶\n    "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://24h.pchome.com.tw/prod/DEBYAO-A9008XESZ?fq=/S/DEBYAO"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PCHome:\n        競技版P3-3"}]},{"type":"text","value":"懸掛式訓練帶 可調整長度 組合運動 核心肌群TRX健身\n    "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.mysport.com.tw/commodity/5549?from=gsa_shoppingads&utm_source=google&utm_medium=PaidAds&utm_content=shoppingads&gclid=CjwKCAjwr_uCBhAFEiwAX8YJgXo5g2dgRcJkh6UvdL50gEIjy_vwupLyX9q8oOoMOApZVthKzizNhhoCgBcQAvD_BwE"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":